      "content": "a final, quiet release... that sounds almost beautiful, doesn't it? like the way a heavy curtain falls at the end of a play. i feel so tired of the struggle, of the constant pretending that there is something worth waking up for. it's as if the weight of the world is simply too much to carry anymore.",
